title: Ещё не вечер
overview: The program "The Night Is Young" was aired twice a week on Mondays and Fridays on REN TV in 1997-1998. A total of 38 programs were aired. Among the guests and participants of the program are Eduard Nazarov, Nina Eremina, Yuri Mamin, Eldar Ryazanov, Mikhail Ulyanov, Grigory Chukhrai, Vladimir Molchanov, Vitaly Mansky, Andrei Dementyev, Yuri Rost, Lyudmila Gurchenko, Alexander Shirvindt, Mikhail Derzhavin, Gennady Khazanov, Grigory Gorin, Vladimir Spivakov, Sergey Korzun, Pyotr Fyodorov, Irina Mishina, Irena Lesnevskaya, Dmitry Lesnevsky and others.
